04:33.240 --> 04:35.208
Greetings, Martha.

04:36.240 --> 04:36.843
Greetings.

04:38.040 --> 04:43.524
You should hurry home,
it's getting dark already.

04:46.640 --> 04:50.087
It's Twelfth Night tonight.

04:50.600 --> 04:55.128
Watch out that Perchta doesn't get you.

04:58.960 --> 05:00.564
Yes yes, Sepp.

09:18.960 --> 09:21.247
You should be burned down, you witches.

09:24.320 --> 09:26.402
We'll get you.

11:17.840 --> 11:19.046
Mother.

11:54.840 --> 11:58.731
Albrun, I.

17:07.720 --> 17:09.559
Mother, please.

17:09.560 --> 17:12.165
You have to eat at least a little bit.

17:18.839 --> 17:20.683
Albrun.

17:58.720 --> 18:00.722
Eat some more.

19:11.760 --> 19:15.048
Albrun. It's so dark.

19:15.200 --> 19:17.328
It's alright, it's alright.

20:20.840 --> 20:22.524
Albrun.

20:50.280 --> 20:51.566
Come Albrun.

20:52.840 --> 20:53.762
Come.

26:04.920 --> 26:13.249
HORN

29:35.680 --> 29:37.284
Go back to where you came from.

29:39.280 --> 29:41.169
Nobody wants your rotten milk here.

29:42.000 --> 29:43.650
You ugly witch!

29:48.840 --> 29:50.126
Those spoil boys.

29:58.560 --> 30:00.528
You live in the the hut
next to the creek, right?

30:04.720 --> 30:06.722
Hey Swinda.

31:20.040 --> 31:21.326
Albrun.

31:31.920 --> 31:32.967
Albrun.

31:41.680 --> 31:42.567
Hello.

31:47.560 --> 31:49.324
The priest sent me.

31:49.720 --> 31:50.926
He said you should come down to see him.

31:52.920 --> 31:54.285
He'd like to have a word with you.

32:00.000 --> 32:01.206
I'll walk with you.

32:11.840 --> 32:13.842
Why are you up here all by yourself?

32:16.640 --> 32:20.611
I couldn't do that. With a child and all.

32:25.160 --> 32:26.571
Where's your husband?

32:31.840 --> 32:33.285
There is none.

34:04.840 --> 34:08.208
As I began serving this community,

34:11.440 --> 34:15.842
I was full of hope for my mission

34:19.120 --> 34:25.321
to sink the light of faith in our holy
church deep into the hearts of the people.

34:27.639 --> 34:30.928
People like you, Albrun,

34:33.639 --> 34:41.239
whose path is paved with
suffering and pain.

34:51.760 --> 34:54.445
The morbid case of your mother

34:56.280 --> 35:00.001
and your secluded way of life.

35:02.160 --> 35:10.807
A way of life that already tempted
many believers to touch the darkness.

35:13.040 --> 35:19.844
A touch that sprung from sacrilege.

35:36.960 --> 35:40.601
But to strengthen the
faith of an righteous community

35:42.120 --> 35:47.331
it requires all sacrilege be cleansed.

41:49.280 --> 41:50.008
Albrun.

42:02.080 --> 42:02.569
Hello.

42:04.040 --> 42:04.563
Hello.

42:06.320 --> 42:08.322
I thought I'd come visit you.

42:11.520 --> 42:11.964
Yes.

42:41.440 --> 42:42.930
What is her name?

42:44.240 --> 42:47.801
Martha, like her grandmother.

42:56.320 --> 42:58.163
She looks so healthy.

43:33.760 --> 43:35.922
I nearly forgot.

43:37.920 --> 43:40.844
I found such a pretty one,
thought I would bring it for you.

43:42.840 --> 43:44.126
Thank you.

44:54.320 --> 44:56.607
I have to go look after
my children as well.

45:05.040 --> 45:08.726
It was nice to see you, Swinda.

45:14.280 --> 45:15.247
I think so too.

45:16.040 --> 45:17.007
See you soon.

51:48.840 --> 51:52.845
We really do have
a nice spot here in our mountains.

52:06.640 --> 52:08.051
We don't have to be afraid here.

52:12.000 --> 52:14.526
Afraid? Of what?

52:18.800 --> 52:22.327
Of those who don't
carry Gods light in their hearts.

52:24.320 --> 52:26.163
By the jews

52:28.000 --> 52:29.286
and the heathens.

52:48.000 --> 52:49.843
They come at night

52:51.560 --> 52:55.326
and like animals they take you.

53:04.160 --> 53:09.690
And a few months
later you bear a child like that.

54:03.280 --> 54:04.566
That's her.

54:05.440 --> 54:06.282
Albrun.

54:26.720 --> 54:27.562
Come.

55:26.040 --> 55:28.202
It is disgusting how all of you stink.

55:29.240 --> 55:31.049
Your rotten stench.

